generateCombinationList

public static java.util.List<java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>> generateCombinationList(int max)
returns a list of list of integers. Supply it with an integer of the list size and it will return all possible combinations of all groupings of the integers up to the integer you supply thus supplying 3 would return: -- blank entry-- 1 2 3 1 2 1 3 2 3 1 2 3

Parameters:
max -
Returns:
list of all possible integer combinations going from 0 to max.
